      "功能描述": "The general get operation of the external provider. Currently supports the property method names defined in GMT 0016-2023. 1. Error reported when the provider accesses the SKF interface of Ukey. This error may occur if the process function is not found, or due to other issues. 1. The resourceId or propertyId length is invalid. 2. The params contains invalid tags or invalid value types. 1. The provider experienced an internal processing error.",
